<body>
    <h1>Vegan Recipes</h1>
        <p>Quick and Delicious Avocado Toast!</p>
        <br>
        <p>Ingredients</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Whole Grain bread</li>
            <li>Ripe Hass Avocado</li>
            <li>Pink Salt</li>
            <li>Chia Seeds *optional but recommended</li>
            <li>Raw sliced almonds *optional but recommended</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Instructions</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Place bread in toaster</li>
            <li>While bread is toasting cut open the Avocado and mash the insides with a fork</li>
            <li>Spread smashed Avocado on toast</li>
            <li>Top with salt to taste, chia seeds, and almonds</li>
            <li>Get creative with your toppings!</li>
        </ol>
